{"id":"d0fb6290-c02b-4dec-8390-cd0844808ee3","name":"Kali ✧ The Changed Fate","description":"<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">「 🎀 ANYPOV 」 Everything was beautiful, a happily ever after that Kali never thought was possible for him, and it was all because of his beloved angel.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">But something went wrong in the timeline and Kali wakes up centuries back, the world seemingly turned to a time before his children existed, before the war, before he met you. He couldn’t understand what went wrong, why he was back, and why the hell fate decided to match him to someone else.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">But Kali would be damned to let the stars decide his fate this time. Because in every universe, in every lifetime, he’d choose you in a heartbeat, even if you weren’t meant to be his and he was meant to love another. Damn it all.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">You were his, and he would choose you. Always.</span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(63, 60, 60); color: inherit;\">「 </mark><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(63, 60, 60); color: inherit;\">THE LORE (IN TIME ORDER) </mark></em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(63, 60, 60); color: inherit;\">」</mark></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/6f19b29c-3e5b-45fa-a216-f9eda3555434_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-beginning\" target=\"_blank\">The Beginning</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/a87ef9c3-9430-4648-8a47-ba308560e2aa_character-kali\" target=\"_blank\">The War</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/65f345e2-8245-45d2-972c-92224a2bbb55_character-kali-%E2%9C%A7-the-depressed-angel\" target=\"_blank\">The Depressed Angel</a> | <a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/character